{"id":432,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":34,"title":"34. A Lazy Boy","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy.432/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy-2022-03-07-21-16-00/0-34-a-lazy-boy.mp3","transcript":"I'm very angry with my son, Harry.\nWhy? What's the problem?\nHe's not doing well in school.\nThat's a surprise. Harry's a smart boy.\nYes, but he never studies.\nDid you talk to his teachers?\nYes, I did.\nWhat did they say?\nHe's a nice boy, but he's very lazy.\nMaybe they're right.\nI'm afraid so.\nHave you thought about getting him a tutor?\nMaybe that's a good idea; I really want him to excel.\nLet's go look in the phone book now then.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:39","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"I'm very angry with my son, Harry.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy-2022-03-07-21-16-00/1.mp3","time_start":2.2,"time_end":4.44},{"position":2,"content":"Why? What's the problem?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy-2022-03-07-21-16-00/2.mp3","time_start":4.44,"time_end":5.85},{"position":3,"content":"He's not doing well in school.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy-2022-03-07-21-16-00/3.mp3","time_start":5.88,"time_end":7.56},{"position":4,"content":"That's a surprise. Harry's a smart boy.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy-2022-03-07-21-16-00/4.mp3","time_start":7.56,"time_end":9.62},{"position":5,"content":"Yes, but he never studies.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/34-a-lazy-boy-2022-03-07-21-16-00/5.mp3","time_start":9.69,"time_end":11.87},{"position":6,"content":"Did you talk to his teachers?","audio_ur